{"id":"a021","internalId":"2316d1b6-e5b3-417d-9d22-eae327dbb7df","createdAt":"2026-01-21T19:33:49.300Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-24T10:39:59.881Z","status":{"code":"PUBLISHED","name":"Published"},"assessmentType":{"code":"CAR_ASSISTED_DRIVING","name":"Car Assisted Driving"},"assessmentDiagrams":[],"publicationDate":"2024-10-23","publicationYear":"2024","ratingYear":2024,"SPRefNumber":"a021","umbracoRefNumber":null,"rescueSheetURL":null,"greenNcapURL":null,"frontalImageURL":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/2316d1b6-e5b3-417d-9d22-eae327dbb7df/VW-ID7__b4e85d8f59417e66_original.png","frontalImage":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/2316d1b6-e5b3-417d-9d22-eae327dbb7df/VW-ID7__b4e85d8f59417e66_original.png","altText":null,"width":1144,"height":760,"formats":{"large":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/2316d1b6-e5b3-417d-9d22-eae327dbb7df/VW-ID7__b20734e59f6bf623_lg.webp","width":1144,"height":760},"small":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/2316d1b6-e5b3-417d-9d22-eae327dbb7df/VW-ID7__0a58de6b61ddb00d_sm.webp","width":320,"height":213},"medium":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/2316d1b6-e5b3-417d-9d22-eae327dbb7df/VW-ID7__29591a916bf39886_md.webp","width":768,"height":510},"xlarge":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/2316d1b6-e5b3-417d-9d22-eae327dbb7df/VW-ID7__b20734e59f6bf623_xl.webp","width":1144,"height":760},"thumbnail":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/2316d1b6-e5b3-417d-9d22-eae327dbb7df/VW-ID7__864cc3c0c5e76c25_thumb.webp","width":156,"height":104}}},"newsMarketURL":"https://news.euroncap.com/safercars/choose-a-car/vw-id.7---euro-ncap-2024-assisted-driving-results---good-grading/s/16e099a2-495b-41e3-8123-650e3d5347e6","resultApplicability":"all","comments":"<p>Volkswagen’s appropriately named Travel Assist’ accurately portrays system functionality. The promotional material and the handbook correctly indicate the limitations of the system capabilities, but a quick-start guide is not available. System status information is clearly displayed. The sensing of hands on the steering wheel was robust, and the system detects driver drowsiness. The system balances driver steering input with lane guidance, promoting co-operative driving.</p><p>The ID.7 combines map-based speed limit information with real time camera inputs to manage fixed, variable and temporary speed limit signs and adapts the speed for upcoming road features such as curves and junctions. The car responds to avoid or mitigate a collision in many of the ACC test scenarios. The driver is supported through the S-Bend, the car being kept fully in lane at the two lowest test speeds. A lane-change assist function is provided. In case of an unresponsive driver, the VW performs a controlled stop within lane. If the radar or camera is blocked the car provides a timely warning and prevents system activation.</p><p>The ID.7 from Vokswagen provides good Vehicle Assistance with a similar level of Driver Engagement. Combined with a high level of safety back-up, the system, overall, offers Good highway assistance.</p>","testedHandOfDrive":null,"assessmentTags":[],"assessmentData":{"carAssistedDriving":{"disclaimer":"When using Assisted Driving Systems (also known as SAE Level 2 systems), a driver’s responsibilities include monitoring the system’s control of speed, braking and steering at all times, strict compliance with traffic rules, and maintaining situational awareness throughout the journey. Certain situations might negatively influence the system’s performance (e.g. poor weather, faded lane markings, construction zones, exiting a tunnel), resulting in a sudden interruption of the lateral and/or longitudinal support (system disengagement). Moreover, the system may fail to detect certain road users such as motorcyclists not directly in front of the vehicle, or stationary objects. Appropriate fitness to drive is critical for safe travel, even when using Assisted Driving Systems. Visual distraction (e.g. eyes off the road), impairment (e.g. drowsiness, intoxication) as well as unresponsiveness, poses high risks. It is highly recommended to keep your hands on the steering wheel at all times to ensure immediate reaction when the system disengages.","domain":{"highway":"RECOMMENDED","interUrban":"RECOMMENDED","urban":"NOT_RECOMMENDED"},"nicePublicationDate":"October 2024","assistedDrivingPerformance":{"assistanceCompetence":{"score":70,"maxScore":100,"normalisedScore":70,"driverEngagement":{"score":70.9,"maxScore":100,"normalisedScore":70.9,"elements":{"consumerInformation":{"score":20,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN","elements":{"marketingMaterial":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-8TeC-hXapo","viewDate":"14/10/2024"},"quickStartGuide":false,"handbook":{"url":"https://euroncap.blob.core.windows.net/media/83433/vw-id-7-2024-a021_vehicle-handbook_travel-assist.pdf"}}},"systemStatus":{"score":22.9,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN","elements":{"continuousSystemStatusIndicator":"GREEN","systemStatusChangeIndicator":"YELLOW"}},"driverMonitoring":{"score":5,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"BROWN","elements":{"handsOnMonitoring":"GREEN","directDriverMonitoring":"RED"}},"drivingCollaboration":{"score":23,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN","elements":{"increaseSteeringTorque":"YELLOW","overrideResponse":"GREEN","comment":"System continues to assist while driver steers to avoid obstacle"}}}},"vehicleAssistance":{"score":84.1,"maxScore":100,"normalisedScore":84.1,"elements":{"speedAssistance":{"score":20.1,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN","elements":{"speedAssistSystems":{"responseToFixedSpeedLimit":"At speed at sign","responseToVariableSpeedLimit":"Slowing down at sign"},"speedLimitInfoFunction":{"generalRequirements":"Compliant","conditionalSpeedLimits":"GREEN","roadFeatures":"YELLOW","localHazards":"GREEN","systemUpdates":"Quarterly"}}},"adaptiveCruiseControlPerformance":{"score":28.9,"maxScore":40,"verdict":"YELLOW","elements":{"scenarios":{"approachingStationaryTarget":{"car":"BROWN","motorCycle":"BROWN"},"approachingSlowerMovingTarget":{"car":"GREEN","motorCycle":"GREEN"},"approachingBrakingTarget":{"car":"GREEN","motorCycle":"GREEN"},"targetCuttingInFront":{"car":"GREEN","motorCycle":"YELLOW"},"carCuttingOutFrontToExposeTarget":{"car":"GREEN","motorCycle":"GREEN"}},"undertakePrevention":{"undertakePreventionSpeedOver90km":"GREEN"},"adaptiveCruiseControlAutoResume":{"assistanceMaintainedAfterFullStop":"GREEN","systemAssistanceMaintained":"Automatic resume with collision prevention by external sensors"}}},"steeringAssistance":{"score":35,"maxScore":35,"verdict":"GREEN","laneChangeAssist":true,"scenarios":{"80km":{"verdict":"GREEN","comment":"Vehicle stays in lane"},"100km":{"verdict":"GREEN","comment":"Vehicle stays in lane"},"120km":{"verdict":"YELLOW","comment":"Vehicle directed in 2nd turn"}}}}}},"safetyBackup":{"score":80,"normalisedScore":80,"elements":{"systemFailure":{"score":25,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN","scenarios":{"sensorBlockedAtStartup":{"camera":{"engagement":"Full blockage after a 5 minute drive","warning":"Yes after sensor blocking"},"radar":{"engagement":"Partial blockage after a 5 minute drive","warning":"Yes after sensor blocking"}},"sensorBlockedVehicleMovingSystemInactive":{"camera":{"engagement":"Full blockage after a 5 minute drive","warning":"Yes after sensor blocking"},"radar":{"engagement":"After a 5 minute drive","warning":"After sensor blocking"}},"sensorBlockedVehicleMovingSystemActive":{"camera":{"engagement":"Full blockage within 2 minutes after blocking","warning":"After sensor blocking"},"radar":{"engagement":"Partial blockage after sensor blocking","warning":"After sensor blocking"}}}},"unresponsiveDriverIntervention":{"score":20,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN"},"collisionAvoidance":{"score":35.6,"maxScore":50,"verdict":"YELLOW","scenarios":{"approachingStationaryTarget":{"car":"BROWN","motorcycle":"RED"},"app